thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Julie

author: Julie
title: Julie
text: I am a first time customer of the Spa Store. I was very pleased, they had what I was looking for, it was easy to find, reasonably priced and they offer fast and free shippping. I also received a one off discount as a new spa owner which I appreciated. Spa store makes shopping for my spa supplies easy!
